{"tid":1182003,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"依家先知我個樣原來好有問題","createTime":"2019-06-02T00:40:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T12:04:53.000Z","uid":195944,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2ef1a7829bc962f61c52babe7b35184a745459ab","tid":1182003,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T00:40:06.000Z","msg":"坐巴士無人會坐旁邊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前幾日落雨 諗住好心遮住啲無遮嘅人 點知佢地寧願全身濕晒 一枝箭咁走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等車時諗住望下架車到未 點知企我後面個女人即刻戴口罩 走咗去隊尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來我真係咁樣衰<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/poison.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/poison.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/poison.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/poison.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/poison.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/poison.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/poison.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/poison.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/poison.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/poison.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無人都有差唔多嘅經歷？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/south_bear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e94dfac7d44b2535ca2fb4eab0203065a8e97a08","tid":1182003,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T00:42:56.000Z","msg":"上次開咗個post話我同事個口好臭<br />\n<br />\n同其他人講返 佢地無出聲 你眼望我眼<br />\n<br />\n我就知有問題個一個係我自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\